                "text": "My skin tingles."
            },
            {
                "speaker": "Narrator",
                "text": "My thoughts dissolve."
            },
            {
                "speaker": "Staff",
                "text": "Welcome home."
            },
            {
                "speaker": "Narrator",
                "text": "===================="
